    def sublist_max(profits):
    # ì½”ë“œë¥¼ ì‘ì„±í•˜ì„¸ìš”.
    max_result = 0
    for i in range(len(profits)):
        for j in range(i, len(profits) + 1):
            max_result = max(max_result, sum(profits[i : i+j]))

    return max_result

print(sublist_max([4, 3, 8, -2, -5, -3, -5, -3]))

print(sublist_max([7, -3, 14, -8, -5, 6, 8, -5, -4, 10, -1, 8]))
